com.analog.lyric.dimple.model.transform

Class VariableEliminator.OrderIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.analog.lyric.dimple.model.transform.VariableEliminator.OrderIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<Variable>
    Enclosing class:
    VariableEliminator

    public static class VariableEliminator.OrderIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<Variable>
    Produces a variable elimination order based on a given variable cost function.

    Once iterator has terminated (i.e. hasNext() is false), you can use getStats() to access statistics that can be used to measure the goodness of the resulting ordering.

    See Also:
    VariableEliminator.orderIterator(VariableCost)
